              <description><![CDATA[<p>Last Friday I had a very productive discussion with Tony Hirst (<a href="http://ouseful.info/">Ouseful.info</a>). I ran through some of my research into Javascript versus no-Javascript web beacons (web-bugs). As ever, it was useful to get some objective criticism and validation from a fellow techie!</p>
