              <title>death in passendale</title>
              <link>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/217</link>
              <guid>https://cloudworks.ac.uk/cloud/view/217</guid>
              <description><![CDATA[DVD: 35 minute drama written produced and performed by mental health service users. This play could be reused for the law course. 
After watching the drama students could
search for relevant legislation
listen to podcasts of stakeholders (e.g. other service users, social workers, advocates)
reflect (as an individual student) and post on course forum
tutor moderated discussion
Assignment reflecting on the process and responding to a number of key questions in relation to issues raised by the drama, demonstrating an understanding of the different / competing perspectives
possible other tools - blog; wiki; debate 
[Ali Wyllie]
]]></description>
          <pubDate>Fri, 06 Jun 2008 13:59:42 +0000</pubDate>
